# M6 — Weapon pickups render as atlas sprites on BOTH host and remote
# client. Pair with 2p_pickup_weapon_sprite.host.shot.
#
# The client receives pickup variant + state via the MAP_REQUEST flow
# (level bytes) + per-pickup PICKUP_STATE updates. Identical PNGs at
# the same tick on both sides confirms the wire path delivers the
# WeaponId byte intact.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/client
network connect 127.0.0.1:24081
name ClientB

at 60   shot lobby
at 240  shot match_t240
at 360  shot match_t360
at 540  shot summary
at 600  end

contact_sheet sheet cols 2 cell 1280 720
